msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

msgid "PCBA AOI 软件是一款面向电子制造的智能光学检测系统。 系统以视觉 AI 为核心，提供从自动建模、参数生成到缺陷检测与持续优化的完整流程。 与传统需要频繁手动调参的方式不同，系统可快速适配生产现场，在提升效率的同时确保精度与稳定性。 依托自适应算法与反馈机制，软件既能识别常见与细微缺陷，也能在生产过程中持续学习，提升良率并降低运维成本。"
msgstr "PCBA AOI is an intelligent optical inspection system for electronics manufacturing. Built around visual AI, it provides a complete workflow from automatic programming and parameter generation to defect detection and continuous optimization. Unlike traditional approaches that need frequent manual tuning, it adapts quickly to the production floor, improving efficiency while ensuring accuracy and stability. With adaptive algorithms and a feedback mechanism, the software detects both common and subtle defects and keeps learning during production, raising yield and lowering maintenance cost."

msgid "本章节演示如何使用 AOI 系统快速完成一块 PCB 的建模、检测与反馈流程。"
msgstr "This chapter walks through using the AOI system to quickly complete the modeling, inspection, and feedback flow for one PCB."

msgid "启动软件"
msgstr "Launch the Software"

msgid "在开始之前，建议您进行以下设置以优化性能："
msgstr "Before you start, we recommend the following settings to optimize performance:"

msgid ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"

msgid ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"

msgid "在桌面点击启动器即可启动软件。"
msgstr "Click the launcher on the desktop to start the software."

msgid "启动软件界面"
msgstr "Launcher screen"

msgid "浏览器将自动打开 ``http://localhost:3005/``。 后端默认地址为 ``http://localhost:8000/``。"
msgstr "The browser opens ``http://localhost:3005/`` automatically. The backend defaults to ``http://localhost:8000/``."

msgid "登录界面"
msgstr "Login screen"

msgid "如需更换后端地址，可在登录页点击 :ui-btn:`Change Host Address（更改主机地址）`，在弹窗中填写后端 URL 后保存。"
msgstr "To change the backend address, on the login page click :ui-btn:`Change Host Address`, enter the backend URL in the dialog, and save."

msgid "更改主机地址"
msgstr "Change host address"

msgid "如需从其他设备访问，将 ``localhost`` 替换为目标机器的 IP。"
msgstr "To access from another device, replace ``localhost`` with the target machine's IP."

msgid "登录与设置"
msgstr "Login and Settings"

msgid "首次进入可以使用 **管理员** 账号登录：用户名 **admin**，密码在部署时提供。"
msgstr "On first use, log in with the **administrator** account: username **admin**, password provided at deployment."

msgid "登录后，点击右上角的 :ui-btn:`齿轮图标` 进入 :ui-tab:`设置` 页面。设置页左侧分为 :ui-tab:`团队`、:ui-tab:`管理模型`、:ui-tab:`系统设置` 等分组。"
msgstr "After logging in, click the :ui-btn:`gear icon` in the top-right to open the :ui-tab:`Settings` page. The left side of Settings is divided into :ui-tab:`Team`, :ui-tab:`Manage Models`, :ui-tab:`System Settings`, and other groups."

msgid "设置界面"
msgstr "Settings screen"

msgid "在左侧展开 :ui-tab:`系统设置`，选择 :ui-tab:`语言`，即可在 :ui-param:`系统语言` 中切换界面语言（如 :ui-opt:`English` / :ui-opt:`中文`）。语言设置会保存在系统中，并在系统重启后生效。"
msgstr "Expand :ui-tab:`System Settings` on the left and pick :ui-tab:`Language`; then switch the UI language under :ui-param:`System Language` (e.g. :ui-opt:`English` / :ui-opt:`中文`). The choice is saved and still applies after a system restart."

msgid "语言设置"
msgstr "Language setting"

msgid "更多设置选项请参见 :ref:`系统管理` 章节。"
msgstr "For more settings, see the :ref:`系统管理` chapter."

msgid "注册产品"
msgstr "Register a Product"

msgid "在主页点击 :ui-btn:`训练PCBA`，注册新的 PCBA/产品，进入 :ui-tab:`自动编程向导`。向导分为 5 个步骤：**基本信息**、**将 PCB 放置在传送带上**、**获取尺寸**、**拍摄**、**添加 CAD（可选）**。"
msgstr "On the home page click :ui-btn:`Teach PCBA` to register a new PCBA/product and open the :ui-tab:`Auto-Programming Wizard`. The wizard has 5 steps: **Basic Info**, **Place PCB on the Conveyor**, **Get Dimensions**, **Capture**, and **Add CAD (optional)**."

msgid "创建产品-自动编程向导"
msgstr "Create product — Auto-Programming Wizard"

msgid "**1. 基本信息**"
msgstr "**1. Basic Info**"

msgid "输入 :ui-param:`产品名称`；在 :ui-param:`自动编程检测类型` 中按需勾选关注的检测项（如 :ui-opt:`本体`、:ui-opt:`极性`、:ui-opt:`焊点`、:ui-opt:`焊盘沾胶`、:ui-opt:`IC 引脚`、:ui-opt:`文字` 等）；如有需要，可在 :ui-param:`自动编程参数` 中开启 :ui-opt:`桥接` 检测并设置 :ui-param:`邻近距离（像素）` 阈值。完成后点击 :ui-btn:`下一步`。"
msgstr "Enter the :ui-param:`Product Name`; under :ui-param:`Auto-Programming Inspection Types`, tick the checks you care about (e.g. :ui-opt:`Mount`, :ui-opt:`Polarity`, :ui-opt:`Solder`, :ui-opt:`Glue on Pad`, :ui-opt:`IC Lead`, :ui-opt:`Text`); if needed, enable :ui-opt:`Bridge` detection under :ui-param:`Auto-Programming Parameters` and set the :ui-param:`Neighbor Distance (px)` threshold. Click :ui-btn:`Next` when done."

msgid "创建产品-基本信息"
msgstr "Create product — Basic Info"

msgid "**2. 将 PCB 放置在传送带上**"
msgstr "**2. Place PCB on the Conveyor**"

msgid "选择对应传送带并点击 :ui-btn:`锁定传送带`，确认或输入传送带宽度后点击 :ui-btn:`进板`，PCB 将自动输送至相机下方的拍摄/定位区域；到位后点击 :ui-btn:`下一步`。"
msgstr "Select the conveyor and click :ui-btn:`Lock Conveyor`; confirm or enter the conveyor width, then click :ui-btn:`PCB In`. The PCB is fed automatically to the capture/positioning area under the camera; click :ui-btn:`Next` once it is in place."

msgid "创建产品-将 PCB 放置在传送带上"
msgstr "Create product — Place PCB on the Conveyor"

msgid "**3. 获取尺寸**"
msgstr "**3. Get Dimensions**"

msgid "若已知 PCB 尺寸，直接输入其宽度与高度（单位：mm）。若尺寸不确定，可移动相机分别拍摄 PCB 左下角与右上角，在图像上依次点击这两个位置并选择 :ui-btn:`自动计算`，系统将自动推算尺寸。"
msgstr "If you know the PCB size, enter its width and height (mm) directly. If not, move the camera to capture the PCB's bottom-left and top-right corners, click those two points on the image, and choose :ui-btn:`Auto-Calculate`; the system computes the size."

msgid "创建产品-获取尺寸"
msgstr "Create product — Get Dimensions"

msgid "**4. 拍摄**"
msgstr "**4. Capture**"

msgid "点击 :ui-btn:`拍摄`，系统将联动相机与传送带分区采集并自动拼接生成完整 PCB 图像；随后框选用于自动编程的有效区域（通常为整板；若需排除治具/夹具边缘，可适当收缩）。该基准图像将作为后续自动编程、对齐与检测的参考，尽量使用洁净、无缺陷的 **Golden board（良品板）** 拍摄。此界面可实时调整相机参数（:ui-param:`曝光时间`、:ui-param:`增益`、:ui-param:`gamma` 等）；如效果不佳，可重新拍摄覆盖上一版本。"
msgstr "Click :ui-btn:`Capture`; the system drives the camera and conveyor to capture in segments and auto-stitches a full PCB image. Then box the valid area for auto-programming (usually the whole board; shrink it to exclude fixture/jig edges if needed). This reference image is used for later auto-programming, alignment, and inspection, so capture a clean, defect-free **Golden board**. You can adjust camera parameters live here (:ui-param:`Exposure Time`, :ui-param:`Gain`, :ui-param:`gamma`, etc.); if the result is poor, re-capture to overwrite the previous version."

msgid "创建产品-拍摄"
msgstr "Create product — Capture"

msgid "**5. 添加 CAD（可选）**"
msgstr "**5. Add CAD (optional)**"

msgid "提供 CAD（``.csv``）文件后，系统可自动读取封装(Package)、丝印/标识、料号(PN)、X/Y 坐标与旋转角度，并按封装或料号聚类，使同类元件一次建模、加速训练，同时减少后续人工分组与命名工作。"
msgstr "After providing a CAD (``.csv``) file, the system reads Package, silkscreen/designator, Part No (PN), X/Y coordinates, and rotation, and clusters by package or part number so identical components are modeled once — speeding up training and reducing later manual grouping and naming."

msgid "上传 ``.csv`` 文件后点击 :ui-btn:`预览表格`，在字段映射界面依次指定：料号(PN)、封装(Package)、X、Y、旋转(°)，（可选）层/板面字段；选择坐标单位（mm 或 mil），确认原点与方向一致，随后点击 :ui-btn:`运行自动编程`。若 CAD 与拍摄图像未正确重合，可在对齐界面通过旋转、平移、缩放微调后重新运行。"
msgstr "After uploading the ``.csv``, click :ui-btn:`Preview Table` and, in the field-mapping view, assign: Part No (PN), Package, X, Y, Rotation (°), and (optionally) layer/side fields; pick the coordinate unit (mm or mil), confirm the origin and orientation match, then click :ui-btn:`Run Auto Programming`. If the CAD and captured image do not align, adjust by rotate / translate / scale in the alignment view and re-run."

msgid "若不提供 CAD，后续自动编程仍可执行；检测质量不受影响，仅失去基于封装/料号的聚类加速，系统将对元件逐一建模。自动编程耗时约 30 秒。"
msgstr "Without CAD, auto-programming still runs; detection quality is unaffected — you only lose package/part-based clustering, and the system models each component individually. Auto-programming takes about 30 seconds."

msgid "创建产品-添加 CAD"
msgstr "Create product — Add CAD"

msgid "产品编程页面"
msgstr "Product Programming Page"

msgid "自动编程完成后，会进入 :ui-tab:`产品编程页面`。顶部提供多个标签页："
msgstr "After auto-programming finishes, the :ui-tab:`Product Programming Page` opens. The top offers several tabs:"

msgid ":ui-tab:`标记/对齐 PCB`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Mark / Align PCB`"

msgid ":ui-tab:`模板编辑器`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Template Editor`"

msgid ":ui-tab:`PCB 拼板`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`PCB Array`"

msgid ":ui-tab:`整板检测`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Whole Board Inspection`"

msgid "左侧还可在 :ui-tab:`设置（Recipe）` 与 :ui-tab:`元件（Component）` 视图之间切换。"
msgstr "On the left you can also switch between the :ui-tab:`Recipe` and :ui-tab:`Component` views."

msgid "**标记/对齐 PCB**："
msgstr "**Mark / Align PCB**:"

msgid "点击 :ui-btn:`+ 标记`，在 PCB 上 **对角位置** 分别框选 2 个固定的参考标记点（圆形、矩形或复杂图案均可）。框选区域应略大，以保证在轻微位移情况下仍能正确定位。当前版本最多支持 2 个 mark 点。如使用 A/B 面双产品检测，可另外点击 :ui-btn:`+ 独特标记` 在每个产品上标记一处差异明显的区域，便于系统自动区分 A/B 面。"
msgstr "Click :ui-btn:`+ Mark` and box two fixed reference marks at **opposite corners** of the PCB (circular, rectangular, or a complex pattern). Make the boxes slightly larger so positioning still works under a small shift. The current version supports at most 2 mark points. For A/B-side mixed-product inspection, also click :ui-btn:`+ Unique Marker` to mark a clearly different area on each product, so the system can tell the A/B sides apart."

msgid "标记对齐示例"
msgstr "Mark / align example"

msgid "**模板编辑器**："
msgstr "**Template Editor**:"

msgid "左侧显示自动编程获得的元件列表（可在 :ui-opt:`元件` / :ui-opt:`料号` 之间切换）。若上传了 CAD，系统会自动显示丝印/标识并将同类元件分组。可通过搜索栏过滤存在问题的项；对于标记不正确的元件，可手动删除并重新编程。"
msgstr "The left shows the component list from auto-programming (switch between :ui-opt:`Component` / :ui-opt:`Part No`). If CAD was uploaded, the system shows silkscreen/designators and groups identical components. Use the search bar to filter problem items; for incorrectly marked components, delete and re-program manually."

msgid "模板编辑器示例"
msgstr "Template Editor example"

msgid "有关手动编程的详细步骤与编辑工具用法，请参见 :ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`。"
msgstr "For detailed manual-programming steps and editing tools, see :ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`."

msgid "训练和评估"
msgstr "Training and Evaluation"

msgid "确认全部元件框与属性无误后，在 **元件列表** 上方点击 :ui-btn:`训练` 按钮启动模型训练，耗时约 1 分钟；训练完成后再点击 :ui-btn:`自动生成检测参数` 按钮，系统会基于当前模板与训练结果生成一套初始检测参数。需要批量评估所有元件时，点击列表上方的 :ui-btn:`三角形箭头` 即可一键评估。"
msgstr "After confirming all component boxes and attributes, click the :ui-btn:`Train` button above the **component list** to start model training (~1 minute); when done, click :ui-btn:`Generate Detection Params` to generate an initial parameter set from the current template and training results. To evaluate all components at once, click the :ui-btn:`triangle arrow` above the list."

msgid "评估完成后，元件会以颜色标记（绿：健康；红：不健康）。可按需查看不健康项并参考 :ref:`检测参数` 继续微调。"
msgstr "After evaluation, components are color-coded (green: healthy; red: unhealthy). Review unhealthy items as needed and fine-tune per :ref:`检测参数`."

msgid "开始检测"
msgstr "Start Inspection"

msgid "返回主页：点击左上角 Logo 回到主页，点击 :ui-btn:`新建检测任务`。在弹窗中完成任务配置："
msgstr "Back to home: click the logo in the top-left to return home, then click :ui-btn:`New Inspection Task`. Configure the task in the dialog:"

msgid ":ui-param:`传送带`：选择传送带；"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Conveyor`: choose the conveyor;"

msgid ":ui-param:`选择一个 PCBA`：选择已编程的产品；"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Select a PCBA`: pick a programmed product;"

msgid ":ui-param:`选择任务模式`：选择任务模式（如 :ui-opt:`自动连续运行任务`）；"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Select Task Mode`: pick a task mode (e.g. :ui-opt:`Auto Continuous Run`);"

msgid ":ui-param:`以演示模式运行`：对同一块 PCB 自动连续运行检测，每隔约 5 秒触发一次。适合熟悉复检/反馈流程或现场演示，无需反复手动触发。"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Run in Demo Mode`: continuously re-inspects the same PCB, triggering about every 5 seconds. Good for learning the review/feedback flow or for on-site demos, with no repeated manual triggering."

msgid "完成后点击 :ui-btn:`开始检测`。"
msgstr "Click :ui-btn:`Start Inspection` when done."

msgid "新建检测任务"
msgstr "New inspection task"

msgid "进入 :ui-tab:`检测页面` 后："
msgstr "Once on the :ui-tab:`Inspection Page`:"

msgid "按空格键，或按设备上的 **进板** 实体按键：进板并立即开始检测。更多快捷键请参见 :ref:`快捷键` 章节。"
msgstr "Press the spacebar, or the physical **PCB In** button on the machine: feeds the board and starts inspection immediately. For more shortcuts, see the :ref:`快捷键` chapter."

msgid "右侧信息栏：实时显示产品统计（合格/不合格）、元件合格率/不良率/误报率与检测时长（可在整板/子板之间切换）。"
msgstr "Right-hand info panel: shows live product stats (pass/fail), component pass/defect/false-call rates, and inspection time (switchable between whole board and sub-board)."

msgid "检测页面"
msgstr "Inspection page"

msgid "检测到缺陷的元件会被标记，可查看放大图、定位框、缺陷类型及判定依据，并立即反馈。反馈后的数据会写入数据集，供后续持续优化使用。"
msgstr "Components with detected defects are flagged; you can view the zoomed image, bounding box, defect type, and the basis for the decision, and give feedback immediately. Feedback is written to the dataset for ongoing optimization."

msgid "复检页面整体视图"
msgstr "Review page overview"

msgid "查看检测历史"
msgstr "View Inspection History"

msgid "在主页点击 :ui-btn:`工作列表` 进入 :ui-tab:`数据分析报告`。页面包含 :ui-tab:`总结`、:ui-tab:`检测结果`、:ui-tab:`不良元件`、:ui-tab:`误判元件` 等标签，并可按 :ui-opt:`今天` / :ui-opt:`昨天` / :ui-opt:`本周` / :ui-opt:`本月` / :ui-opt:`今年` 过滤。"
msgstr "On the home page click :ui-btn:`Work List` to open the :ui-tab:`Data Analysis Report`. The page has tabs such as :ui-tab:`Summary`, :ui-tab:`Inspection Result`, :ui-tab:`Defective Components`, :ui-tab:`False Calls`, and can be filtered by :ui-opt:`Today` / :ui-opt:`Yesterday` / :ui-opt:`This Week` / :ui-opt:`This Month` / :ui-opt:`This Year`."

msgid ":ui-tab:`总结` 提供 OK/NG 数量与比例、告警/误报的 PPM、DPU 等总览指标，以及 NG/OK 比例图。"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Summary` gives overview metrics — OK/NG counts and ratios, alarm/false-call PPM, and DPU — plus an NG/OK ratio chart."

msgid "数据分析报告-总结"
msgstr "Data Analysis Report — Summary"

msgid "切换到 :ui-tab:`检测结果`，可查看每次检测记录：PCBA 名称、序列号、元件数、不良/告警元件数、检测起止时间等。点击某条记录的 :ui-btn:`查看` 进入复检详情。"
msgstr "Switch to :ui-tab:`Inspection Result` to see each inspection record: PCBA name, serial number, component count, defective/alarm component counts, start/end time, etc. Click :ui-btn:`View` on a record to open the review detail."

msgid "检测结果列表"
msgstr "Inspection result list"

msgid "在复检详情中，左侧列出不良元件，中部与右侧展示整板及缺陷的放大图、定位框、缺陷类型与判定依据，并可直接反馈。"
msgstr "In the review detail, the left lists defective components, while the center and right show the whole board and zoomed defects with bounding boxes, defect types, and decision basis; you can give feedback directly."

msgid "复检详情与反馈"
msgstr "Review detail and feedback"

msgid "提交的反馈会写入数据集，用于后续再训练与参数自适应迭代。"
msgstr "Submitted feedback is written to the dataset for later retraining and adaptive parameter iteration."

msgid "迭代模型"
msgstr "Iterate the Model"

msgid "反馈写入数据集后，回到 :ui-tab:`产品编程页面` 重新训练并评估，针对仍为红色的异常元件微调参数即可完成一次迭代。"
msgstr "After feedback is written to the dataset, return to the :ui-tab:`Product Programming Page` to retrain and evaluate; fine-tune parameters for components still marked red to complete one iteration."

msgid "在复检页提交反馈后，也可直接点击 :ui-btn:`AI 更新（AI Update）` 一键据反馈更新检测参数并重训，再点 :ui-btn:`应用参数更新（Apply Param Updates）` 并重新加载会话即可生效，无需回到编程页。"
msgstr "After submitting feedback on the review page, you can also click :ui-btn:`AI Update` to update detection parameters and retrain from the feedback in one click, then click :ui-btn:`Apply Param Updates` and reload the session to apply — no need to go back to the programming page."

msgid "以上即为快速开始全部流程，感谢您的使用。后续更多功能与更详细的说明请继续阅读完整用户手册。"
msgstr "That completes the Quick Start flow. Thank you for using the system. For more features and detail, continue with the full user manual."
